    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the technique of making measurements by using photography. It usually refers to this technique as applied to mapmaking, measuring site elements, and surveying.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a la técnica de hacer mediciones usando la fotografía. Usualmente se refiere a esta técnica como aplicada a la cartografía, elementos de medición de sitio y exámenes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
